# Ludo Multiplayer Game

This is a React-based Ludo multiplayer game with:
- 2-6 player support
- Coin system
- Dice control for master user
- Firebase real-time database integration

## Setup

1. Run `npm install` to install dependencies.
2. Set up your Firebase configuration in `src/firebase/config.js`.
3. Run `npm start` to start the development server.

## Features

- Real-time multiplayer using Firebase
- Master dice control at `/ludo-king-premium`
- Coin tracking system
- Animated game board

Enjoy playing!
